Description: Egypt, view across river, Luxor. Small group of adult males sitting on beach on near side. Wearing gowns, turbans. Wooden cages [?] on ground next to males. Buildings and trees on opposite bank. Medium: Gelatin silver print.
Producer name: Photographed by: John Frederick Clifford Hunt
Curator's comments: Circumstances: The Imperial War Museum holds photographs from the same collection with a more military content - see [HUN-] PIC DOC 66.
